message:
Toriel led Casey into the warm, cozy kitchen of the cottage. The walls were lined with shelves full of cookbooks, and the aroma of sweetness filled the air. She had baked a beautiful, multi-tiered cake with pink frosting and sprinkles, and on top of it, she had placed something unexpected. "Look what I've made," she said with a giggle, her eyes twinkling with excitement. "I've been waiting to give you this surprise for a long time, my dear."

The cake was decorated with a pair of her favorite lacy panties, which she had playfully placed as a garnish. "These are my most delicate pair," she whispered into his ear, her breath hot and sweet. "And I want you to have them, as a symbol of our... special bond."
